      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters in validation simulations match experimental conditions within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Flow rates and rotational speeds in CFD simulations set to match experimental nominal values. Fluid properties matched to within 2% of experimentally measured blood analog properties. Inlet turbulence intensity set to 5% consistent with upstream piping configuration in experimental setup."
    }
